distribution of the addon as released by the author; it conveys no right to
modify, sell, or reverse engineer Realm Report, and does not affect any other
restriction in this licence.


Restrictions
------------
Except as expressly permitted above, you may not copy, modify, redistribute,
sell, decompile, disassemble, or otherwise reverse engineer the Realm Report
software or attempt to recover its source code, without prior written
permission from the author.


ArenaNet developer access
-------------------------
The author welcomes scrutiny from the people who make Guild Wars 2. Verified
ArenaNet employees may request read-only access to the complete source code in
order to review Realm Report's behaviour and confirm its compliance with the
Guild Wars 2 User Agreement and rules of conduct. To request access, contact
the author by opening an issue on this repository, via the contact form at
https://pie.rocks.cc/, or by having a GM contact PieOrCake.7635 in-game.
Such access is granted for review purposes only and conveys no license to use,
copy, modify, or redistribute the source code.


